ZH: 他是一个刻苦学习的学生。
EN: He is a hardworking student.

ZH: 她每天刻苦训练，为了参加比赛。
EN: She trains hard every day in order to participate in the competition.

ZH: 我们需要刻苦努力，才能取得成功。
EN: We need to work hard in order to achieve success.

ZH: 刻苦是他取得进步的秘诀。
EN: Hard work is the secret to his progress.

ZH: 这个工作需要一位刻苦耐劳的人来完成。
EN: This job requires a hardworking and persevering person to complete.

ZH: 她刻苦学习，希望能考上理想的大学。
EN: She studies hard with the hope of getting into her ideal university.

ZH: 他刻苦学习英语，为了能够出国留学。
EN: He studies English diligently with the aim of studying abroad.

ZH: 她的毅力和刻苦工作使得她获得了晋升。
EN: Her perseverance and hard work led to her promotion.

ZH: 他通过刻苦努力，成功地买了自己梦寐以求的车子。
EN: Through hard work and perseverance, he successfully bought the car of his dreams.

ZH: 刻苦是成功的基石。
EN: Hard work is the foundation of success.

